                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宝丽星；跨境电商；创业；品牌资源</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PolyStar; Cross-border electricity suppliers；entrepreneuring；Brand resources</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了宝丽星股份有限公司的创建和早期发展历程。从创建之日起，宝丽星就将自己定位为一家专注于日本品牌海外运营管理服务的国际化企业。宝丽星在经历初期的运营中心选址失策、核心人员招聘失误、品牌导入不当、客户拓展艰难、渠道建设重复等挫折的同时，也在不断学习和调整。在经过团队建设、品牌资源筛选、业务模式创新等一系列改进之后，渐行渐顺。然而，随着4.8跨境电商新政策的落地，危机再次来临，宝丽星又该如何面对新的挑战？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the establishment and early development of PolyStar Co., Ltd. From the establishing of PolyStar, it made itself an international company which was positioning on the overseas operations, management and services of Japan brands. After failing in operation center site selection in initial stage, recruitment mistaking on core personnel, improper brand introduction, tough customer development, and channel construction duplication etc., PolyStar learns and adjusts continuously. After a series of improvement in team construction, brand resources selection, business model innovation, PolyStar becomes smoother running than before. Howeve,with the release of 4.8 Cross-border electricity suppliers’ new policy， the crisis is coming again， how will PolyStar face the new challenge?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
